dct_description_sm: Map shows Indian and military reservation, national parks and forests, private land grants, county and township district boundaries, railroad lines, cities, rivers, lakes, etc. Includes index of 'Mission Indian Reservation, Private Land Grants, and Government Reserves near San Francisco'.
compiled from the official records of the General Land Office and other sources under the supervision of A.F. Dinsmore.
